Dynamics 365 CRM Technical Architect Woking, Surrey, UK Contract Dynamics 365 CRM Technical Architect required for a Dynamics 365 CRM implementation on a 6 month contract basis. The position will fall outside IR35 and will extend into Q2 next year
The programme is working for an insurance company who are undertaking a £15M Digital Transformation Programme, which Dynamics CRM forms a part of.
The role:
- Working within the assurance team as part of the delivery team
- Designing and putting together the architecture documentation for the Dynamics implementation
- Assisting with the integration from Dynamics CRM into 8 Legacy systems
- Assuring the work done by offshore teams and providing direction
- Dynamics CRM 365 Online/Agile and scrum experience required
If this role sounds like it could be of interest, please do click apply and Patrick Eaton from La Fosse give you a call to discuss the role in more detail.
